{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Create a premium, high-converting Black Friday hero promo section for a beauty/e-commerce brand called SIYOU Nails.
    The style should be luxury, feminine, modern, and clean with a soft pink + black color palette, subtle shimmer effects, and elegant typography similar to high-end cosmetic brands.
    
    Include the following elements:
    
    A “LIMITED TIME ONLY” eyebrow text in small caps
    
    A large, bold headline: BLACK FRIDAY SALE
    
    Subheadline: “Get up to 50% off all press-on gel nail sets. Our biggest sale of the year.”
    
    A beautiful animated countdown timer (days / hours / minutes / seconds)
    
    A luxury-styled CTA button: SHOP NOW
    
    Optional background ideas:
    
    soft spotlight gradient
    
    floating gold sparkles
    
    subtle bokeh
    
    minimal particle glow
    
    Layout must be responsive and optimized for mobile first
    
    Keep the look elevated and professional, similar to Glossier / Dior / Olive & June
    
    Use spacing that feels premium: generous padding, centered content, balanced proportions
    
    Make the entire section visually stronger and more premium than the current version
    
    Overall goal:
    A visually stunning hero section that feels editorial, luxury, and holiday-exclusive, driving urgency and conversion for the Black Friday sale., add a background image and a place to insert the logo 
{% enddoc %}
